  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tJump<br />\n\tThe jumping motion allows the body to temporarily leave the surface, experiencing freedom. Who or what is jumping? Where does the action take place? What was the purpose of the action?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: It jumped high up into the sky... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stallion\" target=\"_blank\">stallion</a> leaping over a fence<br />\n\t2) the high jump and long jump events in a sports meet<br />\n\t3) children playing <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hopscotch\" target=\"_blank\">hopscotch</a> in the playground<br />\n\t4) <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bungee\" target=\"_blank\">bungee</a> jumping<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tFrom the moment the man jumped up because of the spilled drink, the only other patron in the cafe took notice of his frantic acts and thought the situation was rather amusing. While watching all the action, this patron near the window saw something fell out of the man's pocket during his search for the tissue, but the man did not seem to realize. Al thought about calling out to the man, but decided against it, so he finished his drink, got up, and walked towards him. Picking it off the ground, he looked at the item. It was an electronic key card.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161682112673/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718978/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718978\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720860/\">2014年英语四级多少分算过啊？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p487116/\">中国式爱情与婚姻：中国在玩的相亲游戏</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p561030/\">跟《唐顿庄园》学20条英国淑女餐桌礼仪</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720245/\">如何战胜自我怀疑？6大招来帮你</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720955/\">纽约时装周 7个新春桃花妆</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p605583/\">办公室危害健康：工作环境在“谋杀”你！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p587662/\">每天要问自己的5个问题 你的答案是什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720792/\">山羊or绵羊？哭晕的“歪果仁”终于明白了！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p581926/\">面试中如何回答\"你的五年工作规划是什么\"</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
