  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/fanli/201303/d238a8fb-efea-40cc-a81a-a18e059875ba.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 225px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p720203\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tThe England manager Roy Hodgson has made it clear that Rio Ferdinand still has an international future <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/despite\" target=\"_blank\">despite</a> his withdrawal from the World Cup qualifiers with San Marino and Montenegro. The Manchester United <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/defender\" target=\"_blank\">defender</a> travelled to London to explain personally to Hodgson why he couldn't <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/accept\" target=\"_blank\">accept</a> to return to the England <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/squad\" target=\"_blank\">squad</a>. As the BBC's Ian Dennis reports.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;It was during that face-to-face discussion where he explained his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/specific\" target=\"_blank\">specific</a> medical programme which according to Hodgson the details are already in place and because he must follow them, it's not possible for him to travel. I'm told it was a positive meeting between the pair, and Rio Ferdinand wants to be considered for squads in the future. But it's the second defensive blow in less than 24 hours for Roy Hodgson after Michael Dawson's withdrawal yesterday. Steven Caulker has joined Joleon Lescott as additions to the squad.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, arial;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); line-height: 25px; font-family: verdana, arial; t